import React from 'react'
import ScriptTag from 'react-script-tag'
import Header from './_share/Header.js'
import Sidebar from './_share/Sidebar.js'
import Main_content from './_share/Main_content.js'
import Footer from './_share/Footer.js'
import PropTypes from 'prop-types'
import '../../asset/admin/dist/css/adminlte.min.css'

export default ({section}) => {
	return (
			<>
				<Header />
				<Sidebar />
				<Main_content section={section} />
				<Footer />
				<ScriptTag src="admin/plugins/jquery/jquery.min.js" />
				<ScriptTag src="../admin/plugins/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" />
				<ScriptTag src="../admin/plugins/overlayScrollbars/js/jquery.overlayScrollbars.min.js" />
				<ScriptTag src="../admin/dist/js/adminlte.js" />
				<ScriptTag src="../admin/dist/js/demo.js" />
				<ScriptTag src="../admin/plugins/jquery-mousewheel/jquery.mousewheel.js" />
				<ScriptTag src="../admin/plugins/raphael/raphael.min.js" />
				<ScriptTag src="../admin/plugins/jquery-mapael/jquery.mapael.min.js" />
				<ScriptTag src="../admin/plugins/jquery-mapael/maps/usa_states.min.js" />
				<ScriptTag src="../admin/plugins/chart.js/Chart.min.js" />
				<ScriptTag src="../admin/dist/js/pages/dashboard2.js" />
			</>	
	)
}
